downhill pair by our team.

94
00:06:00,420 --> 00:06:01,540
Really ?

95
00:06:01,540 --> 00:06:07,200
Well, he's a little
better than me.

96
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:11,400
I've never heard that the
Speedstars' skill level was so high.

97
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:17,400
Anyway, I can contact the Eight-Six driver you're looking for.

98
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:20,110
He's my best friend.

99
00:06:22,090 --> 00:06:25,000
