you to tell him.

100
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:27,510
Next Saturday
at 10:00 pm...

101
00:06:27,510 --> 00:06:30,250
Next Saturday~~~
at 10:00 pm...?~~~

102
00:06:30,250 --> 00:06:35,350
Nakazato of the Night Kids will be waiting at the peak of Mt. Akina.

103
00:06:35,350 --> 00:06:37,750
``At the peak
of Mt. Akina.''

104
00:06:38,110 --> 00:06:40,140
There'll only
be one race.

105
00:06:40,540 --> 00:06:42,350
Wait...is that...?!

106
00:06:42,350 --> 00:06:43,500
Wait a minute !

107
00:06:44,290 --> 00:06:45,800
Hey...

108
00:06:47,110 --> 00:06:49,450
