driving on Akina ?

116
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:14,590
Nope.

117
00:07:14,590 --> 00:07:15,610
Why not ?

118
00:07:15,610 --> 00:07:18,800
Sorry, but unless I have
a special reason...

119
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:21,250
