out and drive.

120
00:07:21,250 --> 00:07:24,000
Takumi, thanks.

121
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:26,120
Come on in and
have some coffee.

122
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,100
Okay.

123
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:29,120
Hey !

124
00:07:30,250 --> 00:07:32,730
This is bad.
This is really bad.

125
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:36,450
Good work.

126
00:07:36,450 --> 00:07:38,270
Hey, Takumi.

127
00:07:39,270 --> 00:07:41,200
Let me ask
you something.

128
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:47,450
Hypothetically speaking, if a Road Racer challenged you...

129
00:07:47,450 --> 00:07:48,800
...you'd race him,
wouldn't you ?

130
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:53,200
I don't like that,
so I wouldn't.

131
00:07:53,790 --> 00:07:54,910
